/*
 * This Hyperlambda snippet demonstrates how to increment a numeric value in place using the [math.increment] slot.
 * 
 * 1. [.counter:int:0]
 *    * Initializes a node named [counter] with an integer value of 0.
 *
 * 2. [math.increment]
 *    * Increments the value of the [counter] node by 1.
 *    * The expression [x:@.counter] points to the [counter] node, allowing its value to be modified directly.
 */
.counter:int:0
math.increment:x:@.counter